d;">Funktionsweise von Aktivkohlefiltern</span>, die Sie für den privaten Gebrauch zu Hause erwerben können.&nbsp;</span></p></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div data-section-id="pf-15d3" data-pf-type="Section" class="sc-YysaK kYyPCk pf-26_ pf-color-scheme-1 autorenbox"><div style="--cw:1170px" class="sc-ktPOXr dplAGv"><div class="sc-jXbVAB kNtuek pf-27_ pf-r pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-sm:7;--c-md:8;--c-lg:8"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-bDoQz cmNGeH pf-28_ toc"><i class="sc-fvtEUL gsyPji pf-29_ pf-icon-1 pfa pfa-align-justify" data-pf-type="Icon"></i><p class="sc-lnPyOc exfzrW pf-30_ pf-text-1" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-fThTNe cAYhcc pf-32_">Inhalt dieses Artikels</span></p><div data-pf-type="Custom.HTML" class="sc-brPMkR emByB pf-33_">{% render 'toc-v2', color: 'orange', autor: 'TM' %}</div></div></div><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-sm:5;--c-md:2;--c-lg:3"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-bDoQz cmNGeH pf-34_ autoreninfo"><div data-pf-type="Image" class="sc-ihgokY faeooD pf-35_ pf-image-1"><img src="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0278/5483/1715/t/10/assets/pf-72cc608e--albfilterlogokreisweiss2x_1200x.png?v=1614671254" srcSet="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0278/5483/1715/t/10/assets/pf-72cc608e--albfilterlogokreisweiss2x.png?v=1614671254 1536w" width="501" height="501" sizes="(min-width: 1536px) 1536px, (min-width: 1024px) 1280px, (min-width: 640px) 768px, calc(100vw/3)" loading="lazy"/></div><p class="sc-lnPyOc exfzrW pf-36_ pf-text-1 autoreninfo-text" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-fThTNe cAYhcc pf-38_"><span style="font-family: 'Amsi-bold'">Autor: </span><span class="autorname"></span> <br><span style="font-family: 'Amsi-bold'">Position: </span><span class="autorpos"></span><br><span style="font-family: 'Amsi-bold'">Aktualisiert am:</span> {{ article.published_at | date: "%d.%m.%Y" }}<br><br><span 